snippet.title: SKYCURSER - Alpha Gameplay Teaser
snippet.description:
SKYCURSER is a hard-action shooter scheduled for a 2016 arcade-exclusive release. Splatter the mutants. Save the planet. Die a hero.

Video by Justin Lucas. 
Voice-over by Mitchell Lucas.
